  <oversight_info>
    <is_fda_regulated_drug>No</is_fda_regulated_drug>
    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To explore whether gut microbiota would impact CD4 T cells recovery in HIV-infected patients
      on antiretroviral therapy (ART). We prospectively enroll patients initiate ART and collect
      their fecal at followup for one year.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
